title: Lifetime-A Country Christmas Story [2013]
description:
Lifetime-A Country Christmas Story (2013) 

Air Date: 8 Nov 2013

Summary: Musical icon and multiple Grammy Award winner Dolly Parton and Grammy Award nominated R&B singer and producer Brian McKnight star in this Lifetime Original Movie. The film follows a young Appalachian mountain girl (Desiree Ross) as she pursues her dream of becoming a country star.
